{"tid":1689950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戰略檢討post ，全世界入黎，比班和理非知道","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:48:19.000Z","uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f97f784465887eebf3630b307c404de836d465","tid":1689950,"uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD新聞、中國工廠爆炸、360發言等等，關我撚事咩，個個都推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你地，關乎到手足性命既檢討post又唔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地仲想害死幾多手足？<br />\n特別係出去發夢緊既時候<br />\n就唔好撚出D無關痛癢既post啦<br />\n大家focus 係戰略post好過啦！<br />\n自己手足既野又唔關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過左今晚係油尖旺，我發現好多問題出現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689291</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全世界推爆個Post，可能有其他post既內容都類似，但我成個熱門都睇唔到有呢D檢討post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68923653d0d221f227ac5b7c91e67e349c5bb633","tid":1689950,"uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"7bfcc748a438f1ff0a07aa38a2f9c269b79405d2","tid":1689950,"uid":159292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2fb78fb09e8b4adf7a387537ec80ad447f5891c7","tid":1689950,"u